{"type": "root", "attrs": {"type": "node", "context": "sop", "internal": "texture", "icon": "SOP/texture", "tags": "uvs, textures", "version": null, "namespace": null}, "body": [{"level": 0, "type": "title", "indent": 0, "text": ["UV Texture"], "extent": [87, 102]}, {"type": "summary", "indent": 0, "text": ["Assigns texture UV coordinates to geometry\nfor use in texture and bump mapping."], "extent": [102, 190]}, {"type": "para", "indent": 0, "text": ["The UVTexture operation assigns texture UV coordinates to the source\ngeometry for use in texture and bump mapping."], "extent": [190, 306]}, {"type": "note_group", "body": [{"type": "note", "indent": 0, "role": "item", "extent": [306, 312], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["When the projection type is cylindrical or polar, closed mesh, Bezier\n    and NURBS surfaces will be opened. At least one row/column of vertices\n    will be added (possibly more for NURBS). This is to prevent poor\n    interpolation of texture coordinates at the seam of the join."], "extent": [312, 598]}], "container": true}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}, {"type": "tip_group", "body": [{"type": "tip", "indent": 0, "role": "item", "extent": [598, 603], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["Before applying a spline-based texture projection, remap the U\n    and/or V bases of the split surface (using a ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/basis", "type": "link", "text": ["Basis\n    SOP"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/basis"}, ") between 0 and 1 to ensure a complete mapping of\n    the texture. If a single texture map must be shared by several\n    surfaces, the surface bases should be concatenated prior to being\n    remapped."], "extent": [603, 951]}], "container": true}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}, {"type": "box_group", "body": [{"ext": null, "type": "box", "indent": 0, "role": "item", "extent": [16, 22], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["The best way to visualize the effects on UVs is in the UV view. To change a viewport to show UVs, click the View menu in the top right corner of a viewport and choose ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Set View \u25b8 UV viewport"]}, ", or move the mouse over the view and press ", {"keys": ["Space", "5"], "type": "keys", "text": null}, "."], "extent": [46, 303]}, {"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["You can also visualize UV attribute values in the 3D view using an ", {"scheme": null, "value": "/basics/visualizers", "type": "link", "text": ["attribute visualizer"], "fullpath": "/basics/visualizers"}, "."], "extent": [303, 420]}], "container": true, "attrs": {"id": "visualizePara"}}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}, {"level": 2, "id": "includeme", "container": true, "type": "h", "indent": 0, "text": ["Using UV Texture"], "extent": [255, 290], "body": [{"type": "ord_group", "body": [{"blevel": 6, "type": "ord", "indent": 4, "text": ["Select the primitives to compute texture UVs for."], "extent": [290, 361]}, {"blevel": 6, "type": "ord", "indent": 4, "text": ["Click the ", {"scheme": "Icon", "value": "SOP/texture", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/shelf/SOP/texture"}, {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/texture", "type": "link", "text": ["UV Texture"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/texture"}, " tool on the ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Texture"]}, " tab."], "extent": [361, 459]}], "container": true}, {"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["The UV Texture tool allows you to choose a ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Texture Type"]}, " from the drop-down menu in the ", {"scheme": null, "value": "/ref/panes/parms", "type": "link", "text": ["parameter editor"], "fullpath": "/ref/panes/parms"}, ", including Rows & Columns and Perspective from Camera."], "extent": [459, 646]}]}, {"level": 1, "id": "parameters", "container": true, "type": "parameters_section", "indent": 0, "role": "section", "extent": [1029, 1041], "body": [{"type": "parameters_item_group", "body": [{"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 4, "text": ["UV Attribute"], "extent": [1041, 1059], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 8, "text": ["The name of the texture coordinate attribute to create, defaulting to ", {"type": "code", "text": ["uv"]}, "."], "extent": [1082, 1166]}], "container": true, "attrs": {"id": "uvattrib"}, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 4, "text": ["Group"], "extent": [1166, 1177], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 8, "text": ["Subset of geometry to apply texture to."], "extent": [1177, 1225]}], "container": true, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 4, "text": ["Texture Type"], "extent": [1225, 1243], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 8, "text": ["Type of projection to use."], "extent": [1243, 1279]}, {"type": "dt_group", "body": [{"type": "dt", "indent": 8, "text": ["Orthographic"], "extent": [1279, 1301], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 12, "text": ["Direct projection from axis"], "extent": [1301, 1341]}], "container": true}, {"type": "dt", "indent": 8, "text": ["Polar"], "extent": [1341, 1356], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 12, "text": ["Wrap spherically in axis direction"], "extent": [1356, 1403]}], "container": true}, {"type": "dt", "indent": 8, "text": ["Cylindrical"], "extent": [1403, 1424], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 12, "text": ["Wrap cylindrically in axis direction"], "extent": [1424, 1473]}], "container": true}, {"type": "dt", "indent": 8, "text": ["Row & Columns"], "extent": [1473, 1496], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 12, "text": ["For geometry constructed as a mesh. The U coordinates are\n            placed along rows and the V coordinates along columns."], "extent": [1496, 1633]}], "container": true}, {"type": "dt", "indent": 8, "text": ["Face"], "extent": [1633, 1647], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 12, "text": ["Maps a copy of the texture onto every face along its normal,\n            orienting the texture properly. However, the map is not\n            scaled to fit each polygon, nor is it distorted by the shape\n            of each polygon."], "extent": [1647, 1890]}], "container": true}, {"type": "dt", "indent": 8, "text": ["Modify Source"], "extent": [1890, 1913], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 12, "text": ["If the source already has texture UV coordinates, they are\n            maintained but may be scaled and offset. See also ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/uvedit", "type": "link", "text": ["UV\n            Edit"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/uvedit"}, " and ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/uvtransform", "type": "link", "text": ["UV\n            Transform"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/uvtransform"}, "."], "extent": [1913, 2137]}], "container": true}, {"type": "dt", "indent": 8, "text": ["Uniform Spline"], "extent": [2137, 2161], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 12, "text": ["Polygon curves and NURBS/Bezier curves/surfaces only.\n            Samples the basis of each curve or\n            surface uniformly in U and V and assigns those values as\n            texture coordinates to the surface points or vertices."], "extent": [2161, 2410]}], "container": true}, {"type": "dt", "indent": 8, "text": ["Average Spline"], "extent": [2410, 2434], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 12, "text": ["Polygon curves and NURBS/Bezier curves/surfaces only.\n            The coordinates of each\n            control vertex\u2019s Greville point are used as the texture UV."], "extent": [2434, 2608]}], "container": true}, {"type": "dt", "indent": 8, "text": ["Arc Length Spline"], "extent": [2608, 2635], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 12, "text": ["Polygon curves and NURBS/Bezier curves/surfaces only.\n            Samples the basis of each curve or\n            surface based on arc lengths and assigns those\n            values as texture coordinates to the points or\n            vertices."], "extent": [2635, 2888]}], "container": true}, {"type": "dt", "indent": 8, "text": ["Perspective From Camera"], "extent": [2888, 2921], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 12, "text": ["The texture coordinates are assigned so that the world space\n            of the object can be textured to fit the projection of the\n            camera exactly."], "extent": [2921, 3093]}], "container": true}], "container": true}], "container": true, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 4, "text": ["Projection Axis"], "extent": [3093, 3114], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 8, "text": ["Axis to project along, or projection method from splines."], "extent": [3114, 3180]}], "container": true, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 4, "text": ["Camera"], "extent": [3180, 3192], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 8, "text": ["Camera or light to project perspective coordinates from"], "extent": [3192, 3256]}], "container": true, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 4, "text": ["Attribute Class"], "extent": [3256, 3277], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 8, "text": ["Whether the texture is applied to points or vertices."], "extent": [3277, 3340]}, {"type": "dt_group", "body": [{"type": "dt", "indent": 8, "text": ["Auto Select"], "extent": [3340, 3361], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 12, "text": ["Let the operation determine the type of uv attribute\n            created."], "extent": [3361, 3447]}], "container": true}, {"type": "dt", "indent": 8, "text": ["Point"], "extent": [3447, 3462], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 12, "text": ["Create point uv attribute."], "extent": [3462, 3501]}], "container": true}, {"type": "dt", "indent": 8, "text": ["Vertex"], "extent": [3501, 3517], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 12, "text": ["Create vertex uv attribute."], "extent": [3517, 3557]}], "container": true}], "container": true}], "container": true, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 4, "text": ["Scale"], "extent": [3557, 3568], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 8, "text": ["Scales texture coordinates."], "extent": [3600, 3636]}], "container": true, "attrs": {"channels": "/su /sv /sw"}, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 4, "text": ["Offset"], "extent": [3636, 3648], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 8, "text": ["Offsets texture coordinates."], "extent": [3695, 3732]}], "container": true, "attrs": {"channels": "/offsetu /offsetv /offsetw"}, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 4, "text": ["Angle"], "extent": [3732, 3743], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 8, "text": ["Rotates texture coordinates about projection axis."], "extent": [3770, 3829]}], "container": true, "attrs": {"channels": "/angle"}, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 4, "text": ["Fix Boundary Seams"], "extent": [3829, 3853], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 8, "text": ["Makes sure the texture wraps around correctly."], "extent": [3853, 3909]}], "container": true, "role": "item"}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}], "text": "Parameters"}, {"level": 1, "id": "related", "container": true, "type": "related_section", "indent": 0, "role": "section", "extent": [3909, 3918], "body": [{"type": "bullet_group", "body": [{"blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "indent": 4, "text": [{"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/uvpelt", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/uvpelt"}], "extent": [3918, 3942]}, {"blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "indent": 4, "text": [{"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/uvproject", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/uvproject"}], "extent": [3942, 3969]}, {"blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "indent": 4, "text": [{"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/uvquickshade", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/uvquickshade"}], "extent": [3969, 3999]}, {"blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "indent": 4, "text": [{"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/uvunwrap", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/uvunwrap"}], "extent": [3999, 4026]}], "container": true}], "text": "Related"}], "title": ["UV Texture"], "summary": ["Assigns texture UV coordinates to geometry\nfor use in texture and bump mapping."], "included": ["/nodes/sop/texture_common", "/shelf/uvtexture"]}